channel.title: Anyone willing to pay $17?
channel.description:
Okay, first and foremost if you're going to call me a scab piss off.
Now, second. Does anyone have $17 spare on a paypal account, which they could lend me to buy a book. I would be willing to work for it, I just cannot buy it as we do not have a credit card which supports paypal. I have tried downloading it as an e-Book, cracked, etc, but none work, and quite frankly I would rather a hard-cover book anyway.
Now, I can work for it, meaning I could program for you until I work off my debt.
